Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果输得只剩内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿银 今天这次是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是阿初的生日
