Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要打破这个MADAO黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论结局怎样 这都是最后了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要留下遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿银
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长谷川啊
